│      + Is valid and does not modify any assertions in the code.                         │
│      + Fixes the original issue shown in the reproducer.                                │
│      + Does not introduce any new regressions.                                          │
│ 5. **Iterate**: If verification fails, analyze the failure, revise your proposal, and   │
│ repeat the implementation and verification steps until all tests pass.                  │
│ 6. **Submit**: Provide the final, clean patch for review.                               │
